== Description ==

Create store credit style coupons in your WooCommerce store.

See http://www.visser.com.au/wp-ecommerce/plugins/store-credit/

== Installation ==

1. Upload the folder 'woocommerce-store-credit' to the '/wp-content/plugins/' directory

2. Activate 'WooCommerce - Store Credit' through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress

== Usage ==

==== In WooCommerce ====

1. Open WooCommerce > Coupons.

2. Press the 'Add Coupon' button.

3. Type a name for the coupon, and choose 'Store Credit' from the Discount Type drop down menu.

4. Publish the coupon.

5. Add an item to your cart, and use the coupon code to test it out.

That's it!

